      	<div class="page-title" style="margin:0;color:#f7c815;">PRIVACY</div>
        <div style="font-size:1.2em; color:#fff; margin:10px 0 20px 0; line-height:20px;">ProDriver respects your privacy, and takes the responsibility of protecting the personal and business information that you provide to ProDriver  via the ProDriver website (the "Site"), very seriously. To that end ProDriver herein discloses its privacy practices and the possible uses of the information that it gathers via its Site. Please note that ProDriver may update this Privacy Policy from time-to-time at its sole discretion. It is your responsibility to review the Privacy Policy for any changes each time that you use the Site. ProDriver is not a PEO or job placement service and is not liable for expenses incurred, lack of performance of other members and clients or the misrepresentation of abilities or intent of clients or members. 
